posts.title: Arrival in New York
posts.content: Arriving at JFK Airport in New York was an exciting moment as I stepped into the city just before my semester abroad began. The hustle and bustle of the airport, combined with the anticipation of living in the vibrant city, made me eager to start this new chapter of my life.
